Found the cause - when running the whole testing suite, it was being ran in parallel. In Spring Integration testing there are some shared aspects of the context, and thus it caused some errors.
The solution was to add for each testing class like the above the annotation:
@DirtiesContext(classMode=ClassMode.BEFORE_EACH_TEST_METHOD)

